            <title><![CDATA[Hideo Kojima Explains Why He Wants Death Stranding 2 To Be Divisive]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/hideo-kojima-explains-why-he-wants-death-stranding-2-to-be-divisive/1100-6532416/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
